Igihugu cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ni inshingano nk’imwe mu bihugu by’Uburayi na i Ubwami bw’Ubwami bw’Ubwami Bw’Ubwami Bw’Ubwami Bw’Ubwami Bw’Ibyinjijwe Bishimisha ko ku i Igihugu, i Indwara ya COVID- 19 irimo hagati mu byose bihugu.
Ku bihereranye n’ibyabaye mu Butaliyano, ibitaro, ibitaro n’ibintu by’inshingano byagombye gutuma bitegurira abarwayi bafite umutwaro w’abarwayi bafite umutwe w’ubucuruzi ufite n’ubwami bwa COVID-19, bizasaba ubuzima bw’amahanga, kandi cyane cyane ko bazitaho inshingano.
Ku itariki ya 31 Kigarama 2019, mu gihugu cya Hubei mu Bushinwa, havugwaga inshingano y’ibibazo by’ubuhinga bitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, i Center for Control na Prevention yavuze ko i Umuhinga Nka A Ikinyamakuru Coronavirus NONEAHA yavuze ko ari inyuma y'icyuma cya gikomeye cyo kuvugurura 2. (SARS-COV-2).
Uhereye, i indwara yavuye ku SARS-COV- 2 yitwa Coronavirus (COVID- 19).
Ibihamya by’uko abantu bafite COVID-19 bafite indwara y’ubugwaneza, icyo gikaba ari indwara y’impapuro z’impumu cyangwa zitagira impumu, kandi abenshi muri bo bagasubira.
Mu mimerere ya 14%, COVID-19 itera indwara ikomeye cyane isaba gukoreshwa mu bitaro, uko izo zisigaye 6 ku ijana zigera ku ndwara zigoye zisaba kwita ku rugero rukomeye.
Ubwoko bw’abarwayi bavugwa mu bitaro bitewe n’ubwa COVID-19 ni ca 4%.
Muri iyi nyigisho, dusuzumye ibyiyumviro by’ibintu bya COVID-19 muri buri Gihugu cy’Uburayi/Iby’ubutunzi (EU/ETA) n’Ubwami bw’Uburengero (UKU), maze tubigereranya n’icyo gihugu cya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
